    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1069530/extras/8e2e7cd1b8a98812820e5a98045bd935.poster.avif?t=1763038325\" width=616 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1069530/extras/8e2e7cd1b8a98812820e5a98045bd935.webm?t=1763038325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1069530/extras/8e2e7cd1b8a98812820e5a98045bd935.mp4?t=1763038325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事背景</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >时间倒回 80 年代。当时的天才“The Creator”创造出名为“Narita One”的电视游乐器主机以及名为“Narita Boy”的旗舰游戏。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Narita Boy》红极一时！它的游戏卡带在世界各地的实体商品架上都被一扫而空。几周内，《Narita Boy》就成了史上最畅销的电玩游戏，因其挥舞 Techno-sword 满足英雄梦的玩法以及让玩家踏上独一无二的旅程而大受好评。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与此同时，在二进制代码之中的数字王国与现实世界连接了。“Him”返回现世并删除了 The Creator 的记忆。监管程序“Motherboard”与她的手下启动了 Narita Boy 程序。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stallions 即将现身，而 Digital Kingdom 需要一名英雄。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1069530/extras/eb0c45051d3cf1b9591827784293d7f6.poster.avif?t=1763038325\" width=616 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1069530/extras/eb0c45051d3cf1b9591827784293d7f6.webm?t=1763038325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1069530/extras/eb0c45051d3cf1b9591827784293d7f6.mp4?t=1763038325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏内容</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《Narita Boy》中奏出交响乐！这是一场激进的动作冒险，一位传奇的像素英雄受困于 Digital Kingdom 境内，化为区区一道回音。探索隐藏 Techno-sword 背后的秘密，拔剑对抗腐化污秽的恶势力“Stallions”。拯救世界！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>像素完美主义者：</strong> 本游戏是完美主义的“领航员”，手绘动画带来栩栩如生的复古时代影像供您体验。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索 Digital Kingdom 的秘密：</strong> 在这个“大魔域”(※) 中四处冒险，探索损坏的二进制代码最黑暗的深处， </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>彻底发挥 Trichroma 之力：</strong> 装备唯一能消除 Stallion 威胁的武器，举起 Techno-sword 并插入敌人的数字心脏。千万别让这个王国展开“帝国反击战”，做一名真正的“银翼杀手”。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>有着“虎胆龙威”的敌人：</strong> 面对只有从您最黑暗的疯狂梦境中才能想象出的敌人！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>给头目一点字节瞧瞧：</strong> 对抗众多激进无比、所向披靡的头目。打倒 Deadly Crab、DragonBot、Black Rainbow 等等众多头目，成为头目“终结者”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>复古级时代的声音：</strong> 一边穿梭于 Digital Kingdom，一边感受合成器的新鲜浪潮冲刷。还有能送您“回到未来”的超嗨节拍。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1069530/extras/7109bc96a76e73402ad169ef2b2210d6.poster.avif?t=1763038325\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1069530/extras/7109bc96a76e73402ad169ef2b2210d6.webm?t=1763038325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1069530/extras/7109bc96a76e73402ad169ef2b2210d6.mp4?t=1763038325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>※请放心，本游戏的故事不会说不完。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1069530/extras/f7441a342bef13f7bf73b15e6ea21502.poster.avif?t=1763038325\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1069530/extras/f7441a342bef13f7bf73b15e6ea21502.webm?t=1763038325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1069530/extras/f7441a342bef13f7bf73b15e6ea21502.mp4?t=1763038325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
